.da VALUTAANM2 29mm 239mm width 240mm
.da HONBELØB 23mm 247mm width 250mm
.da PÅTEGNING 114mm 251mm width 255mm
.da AFKRYDSNING5 24mm 238mm width 240mm
.da DATOSTED 23mm 251,5mm width 255mm
.da HENVEND 114mm 218mm width 220mm
.da TELEFON 132mm 223,5mm width 220mm
